= The Library

Herein contains relevant information about the government and politics of the Merkopian Federation.

@menu

- @ideologies: **Vital elements of the worldbuliding**
- @government: Merkopian system of government and the most important info about the goverment
- @weimar_timeline: Timeline of the Merkopian Federation before 1266
- @curr_gov: Current government details
